:12:"contributors";a:1:{s:12:"takayukister";a:3:{s:7:"profile";s:43:"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister";s:6:"avatar";s:88:"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bb7bc21850c77e9eb16b44102f4a539d?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g";s:12:"display_name";s:16:"Takayuki Miyoshi";}}s:8:"requires";s:3:"4.9";s:6:"tested";s:5:"5.0.4";s:12:"requires_php";b:0;s:6:"rating";i:84;s:7:"ratings";a:5:{i:5;i:1139;i:4;i:114;i:3;i:45;i:2;i:39;i:1;i:253;}s:11:"num_ratings";i:1590;s:15:"support_threads";i:667;s:24:"support_threads_resolved";i:156;s:15:"active_installs";i:5000000;s:12:"last_updated";s:21:"2018-12-18 6:05pm GMT";s:5:"added";s:10:"2007-08-02";s:8:"homepage";s:25:"https://contactform7.com/";s:8:"sections";a:6:{s:11:"description";s:3128:"<p>Contact Form 7 puede gestionar múltiples formularios de contacto, además, puedes personalizar el formulario y el contenido de los correos electrónicos de manera sencilla mediante un simple marcado. El formulario es compatible con envíos por Ajax, CAPTCHA, filtrado de spam de Akismet y mucho más.</p>\n<h4>Documentación y soporte</h4>\n<p>Puedes encontrar <a href="https://contactform7.com/docs/" rel="nofollow">documentación</a>, <a href="https://contactform7.com/faq/" rel="nofollow">FAQ</a> e información más detallada sobre Contact Form 7 en <a href="https://contactform7.com/" rel="nofollow">contactform7.com</a>. Si no eres capaz de encontrar la respuesta a tu pregunta en las preguntas frecuentes o en la documentación, deberías revisar el <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/">foro de soporte</a> en WordPress.org. Si no localizas ningún tema que ataña a tu problema en particular, abre un nuevo hilo.</p>\n<h4>Contact Form 7 necesita de tu apoyo</h4>\n<p>Es difícil seguir con el desarrollo y el soporte para este plugin gratuito sin las contribuciones de usuarios como tú. Si disfrutas usando Contact Form 7 y lo encuentras útil, por favor considera <a href="https://contactform7.com/donate/" rel="nofollow"><strong>hacer una donación</strong></a>. Tu donación nos ayudará a seguir adelante y apoyará el continuo desarrollo del plugin y un mejor soporte a los usuarios.</p>\n<h4>Avisos de privacidad</h4>\n<p>Con la configuración por defecto, este plugin, por su cuenta, no:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>hace seguimiento oculto de usuarios;</li>\n<li>guarda ningún dato personal de usuarios en la base de datos;</li>\n<li>envía ningún dato a servidores externos;</li>\n<li>usa cookies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Si activas ciertas características de este plugin los datos personales del remitente del formulario de contacto, incluida su dirección IP, pueden enviarse al proveedor del servicio. Por tanto, se recomienda confirmar la política de privacidad del proveedor. Estas características incluyen:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>reCAPTCHA (<a href="https://policies.google.com/?hl=en" rel="nofollow">Google</a>)</li>\n<li>Akismet (<a href="https://automattic.com/privacy/" rel="nofollow">Automattic</a>)</li>\n<li>Constant Contact (<a href="https://www.endurance.com/privacy" rel="nofollow">Endurance International Group</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Plugins recomendados</h4>\n<p>Se recomiendan los siguientes plugins a los usuarios de Contact Form 7:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/flamingo/">Flamingo</a> de Takayuki Miyoshi &#8211; Con Flamingo, puedes guardar los mensajes enviados vía formularios de contacto en la base de datos.</li>\n<li><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/bogo/">Bogo</a> de Takayuki Miyoshi &#8211; Bogo es un plugin multilenguaje directo y claro que no provoca dolores de cabeza.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Traducciones</h4>\n<p>Puedes <a href="https://contactform7.com/translating-contact-form-7/" rel="nofollow">traducir Contact Form 7</a> en <a href="https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/contact-form-7" rel="nofollow"><strong>translate.wordpress.org</strong></a>.</p>\n";s:12:"installation";s:424:"<ol>\n<li>Sube la carpeta completa <code>contact-form-7</code> al directorio <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code>.</li>\n<li>Activa el plugin desde el menú &#8216;Plugins&#8217; de WordPress.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Encontrarás el menú &#8216;Contacto&#8217; en tu panel de administración de WordPress.</p>\n<p>Para un uso básico, puedes echar un vistazo al <a href="https://contactform7.com/" rel="nofollow">sitio del plugin</a>.</p>\n";s:3:"faq";s:444:"<p>¿Tienes preguntas o problemas con Contact Form 7? Utiliza estos canales de soporte apropiadamente.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href="https://contactform7.com/docs/" rel="nofollow">Documentación</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://contactform7.com/faq/" rel="nofollow">FAQ</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/">Foro de soporte</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href="https://contactform7.com/support/" rel="nofollow">Soporte</a></p>\n";s:9:"changelog";s:4837:"<p>Para más información revisa la página de  <a href="https://contactform7.com/category/releases/" rel="nofollow">versiones</a>.</p>\n<h4>5.1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>reCAPTCHA: Modifica la reacción a los tokens de respuesta vacía.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>5.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Introduce el módulo de integración con Constant Contact.</li>\n<li>Actualiza el módulo reCAPTCHA para que sea compatible con reCAPTCHA v3.</li>\n<li>Añade reglas de estilo al modo oscuro.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>5.0.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Se arregla el problema de inconsistencia entre get_data_option() y get_default_option() e la clase WPCF7_FormTag.</li>\n<li>Se suprimen errores PHP que ocurren en las llamadas unlink().</li>\n<li>Se introduce wpcf7_is_file_path_in_content_dir() para compatibilidad con el uso de la constante UPLOADS.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>5.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Especifica explícitamente el argumento capability_type en la llamada register_post_type() para arreglar el problema de la vulnerabilidad de la escalada de privilegios.</li>\n<li>Adjunto de archivo local &#8211; inhabilita especificar las rutas de archivo absolutas referidas a archivos fuera del directorio wp-content.</li>\n<li>Validador de configuración &#8211; añade un elemento de prueba para detectar ajustes de adjuntos con archivo no válido.</li>\n<li>Arregla un fallo en la función JavaScript de los navegadores obsoletos que no son compatibles con el atributo de marcador de posición HTML5.</li>\n<li>Casilla de aceptación &#8211; desactiva la característica de no almacenar de la etiqueta de formulario.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>5.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>CSS: Aplica el estilo de cursor &#8220;not-allowed&#8221; a los botones de enviar en el estado &#8220;inactivo&#8221;.</li>\n<li>Casilla de aceptación: Revisa la interfaz del generador de etiquetas para al uso de mejores opciones en lo que se refiere a la protección de datos personales.</li>\n<li>Introduce la función wpcf7_anonymize_ip_addr().</li>\n<li>Introduce la opción consent_for:storage en todos los tipos de etiquetas de formulario.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>5.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Añadida sección de avisos de privacidad al archivo readme.txt.</li>\n<li>Actualizada la información del contenido de la caja meta.</li>\n<li>Uso de get_user_locale() en vez de get_locale() donde sea más apropiado.</li>\n<li>Casilla de aceptación: Se desactiva el estado de restablecer botones de enviar tras un envío con éxito.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>5.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Solucionados usos incorrectos de _n().</li>\n<li>Validación de la configuración: Conteo incorrecto de alertas solucionado en el panel de la pestaña de Ajustes adicionales.</li>\n<li>Validación de la configuración: Solucionado un tratamiento incorrecto de la etiqueta de correo especial [_site_admin_email] en el campo de la cabecera de correo Desde.</li>\n<li>Casilla de aceptación: Los atributos e id de la clase especificados se aplicaban al elemento HTML incorrecto.</li>\n<li>Validación de la configuración: Cuando hay una cabecera de correo adicional en buzones de correo, como CC o Responder-a, pero no tiene un valor vacío posible, se muestra el error &#8220;Utilizada sintaxis de correo no válida&#8221;</li>\n<li>Especifica explícitamente el cuarto parámetro de add_action() para evitar pasar valores de parámetro no intencionados.</li>\n<li>Comprueba si el directorio de destino está vacío antes de borrar el directorio.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>5.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Ajustes adicionales: on_sent_ok y on_submit han sido eliminados.</li>\n<li>Nuevo ajuste adicional: skip_mail</li>\n<li>Flamingo: el título de canal entrante cambia a la vez que cambia en el título del correspondiente formulario de contacto.</li>\n<li>Eventos DOM: Haz que la API entera responda a la accesibilidad del objeto a través de event.detail.apiResponse.</li>\n<li>Correo HTML: Añade lenguaje relativo al atributo a la cabecera HTML.</li>\n<li>Subir archivos: Se ajusta la aceptación de atributo al campo de subida.</li>\n<li>Presentamos el WPCF7_MailTag class.</li>\n<li>Permite cancelar un intento de envio de correo usando el gancho de acción wpcf7_before_send_mail. También puedes hacer ajustes en el estado y mensaje mediante el gancho de acción.</li>\n<li>Casilla de aceptación: Permite especificar la declaración de condiciones en el apartado de etiquetas del formulario.</li>\n<li>Casilla de aceptación: soporta la opción opcional.</li>\n<li>Nuevas etiquetas de correo especiales: [_site_title], [_site_description], [_site_url], [_site_admin_email], [_invalid_fields], [_user_login], [_user_email], [_user_url], [_user_first_name], [_user_last_name], [_user_nickname] y [_user_display_name]</li>\n<li>Nuevos ganchos de filtro: wpcf7_upload_file_name, wpcf7_autop_or_not, wpcf7_posted_data_{$type} y wpcf7_mail_tag_replaced_{$type}</li>\n<li>Nuevas características de etiquetas: zero-controls-container y not-for-mail</li>\n</ul>\n";s:11:"screenshots";s:225:"<ol><li><a href="https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454"><img src="https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454" alt="screenshot-1.png"></a><p>screenshot-1.png</p></li></ol>";s:7:"reviews";s:15948:"<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">VERY BAD DOCUMENTATION FOR BASIC CONFIGURATION</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/frappi"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2e8896e13f1e06f513cf9e8ce82e044f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2e8896e13f1e06f513cf9e8ce82e044f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/frappi" class="reviewer-name">Florent <small>(Frappi)</small></a> el <span class="review-date">March 18, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Very bad exemple, missing information !</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">The best free Contact Form plugin for WordPress</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/yordansoares"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/940ca4a79fdd1630d25049f2aefb20a5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/940ca4a79fdd1630d25049f2aefb20a5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/yordansoares" class="reviewer-name">YordanSoares</a> el <span class="review-date">March 17, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">I use this plugin for almost my projects and I don\'t ever had any  problems with it. Some of the features of this plugin:\n\n- Easy to use.\n- Compatible with any template.\n- Customizable: CSS, HTML and JS.\n\nThe unique disadvantage CF7 was that you couln\'t save messages in database... until now: Takayuki Miyoshi made a extension called Flamingo that stores all your received messages in database. Also take a look to this one plugin ;)</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Easy use</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ashmtl"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6169d91f9de89705e4201cc93017a40a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6169d91f9de89705e4201cc93017a40a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ashmtl" class="reviewer-name">Ashod <small>(ashmtl)</small></a> el <span class="review-date">March 16, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">My review will be partial because I didn\'t have time to explore the possibilities of the form. For now I am using it for a simple contact form and was able to set it up using my intuition. The same goes for reCAPTCHA setup. The form is well documented and intuitive.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">what a shame</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/getonlinego"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2ffc62c93e952d8cd78d5031174d2f2a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2ffc62c93e952d8cd78d5031174d2f2a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/getonlinego" class="reviewer-name">getonlinego</a> el <span class="review-date">March 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">was a good plugin, is \'garbage\' and useless now since you stuffed up the \'reCaptcha\'... DO NOT UPDATE the app to the latest... 5.05 or earlier only!\n\n...I suggest you find another contact app that is supported and updated properly!</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Excellent</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="5 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="5" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/massimoroccia"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af1ef8266de4cbe3139675a6b1d32f12?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/af1ef8266de4cbe3139675a6b1d32f12?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/massimoroccia" class="reviewer-name">Max.R <small>(massimoroccia)</small></a> el <span class="review-date">March 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">This plugin is just excellent, it works perfectly, exactly what is needed for a very good WordPress contact form.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">The issue with reCaptcha killed the plugin</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/pzanto"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae71e840f593f2f7be98986bc5c66da5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae71e840f593f2f7be98986bc5c66da5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/pzanto" class="reviewer-name">pzanto</a> el <span class="review-date">March 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">What used to be a simple and reliable plugin now its not being able to use anymore in my sites because of the issue with reCaptcha. Sad, i hope gets fixed soon</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Do not use this plugin</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/cirymarr"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/574931d9449699a7f27a38020cd23e2d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/574931d9449699a7f27a38020cd23e2d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/cirymarr" class="reviewer-name">cirymarr</a> el <span class="review-date">March 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Sometimes, we all purchase plugins on the assumption that it will work, and that an acceptable level of support will be provided by the author/developer of said plugin.\n\nContact Form 7 WAS a good plugin for Contact Form creation, until recently, when the developer decided to remove support for reCaptcha V2 and ONLY provide support for reCaptcha V3.  reCaptcha v3, when implemented, results in lots and lots of spam (i.e. it doesn\'t work).  \n\nOnly older versions of Contact Form 7 support reCaptcha V2.  Many customers have posted this issue, but the developer appears to have his head buried in the sand.\n\nMy advice - use another quality Contact Form plugin. I have.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">set up is obtusely difficult</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/flyfisher842"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee2dbdd6d7aed753dbae1691569fd0a0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee2dbdd6d7aed753dbae1691569fd0a0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/flyfisher842" class="reviewer-name">flyfisher842</a> el <span class="review-date">March 7, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">When you have invalid mail syntax, the explanation of how to resolve these errors is obtuse and difficult to understand.  Basically you might as well google for the answer.\n\nwhat used to be simple is not simple any longer</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">From leader to lost plugin</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/jeshl"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a73733ef82f0dd5dc690ce81019c3568?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a73733ef82f0dd5dc690ce81019c3568?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/jeshl" class="reviewer-name">jeshl</a> el <span class="review-date">March 4, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">I imagine at some point you just feel like enough is enough and you stop supporting the plugin right? Made enough money, had enough fun. Been an institution in WPO for a decade. And now they have walked away. Came here looking for fixes to a wpcf7.initForm issue, which was supposedly addressed, but I am still having it. And I read THOUSANDS of other people walking away from cf7. don\'t install this plugin apparently. They went on vacation and aren\'t expected back</div>\n</div>\n<div class="review">\n	<div class="review-head">\n		<div class="reviewer-info">\n			<div class="review-title-section">\n				<h4 class="review-title">Contact form7 with a reCaptcha v3 does not work reliable</h4>\n				<div class="star-rating">\n				<div class="wporg-ratings" aria-label="1 de 5 estrellas" data-title-template="%s de 5 estrellas" data-rating="1" style="color:#ffb900;"><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-filled"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span><span class="star dashicons dashicons-star-empty"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class="reviewer">\n				Por <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/xnosek00"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bccf77c6a02f2a343834d3f6bca2d2cd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bccf77c6a02f2a343834d3f6bca2d2cd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/xnosek00" class="reviewer-name">xnosek00</a> el <span class="review-date">March 3, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class="review-body">Plugin is not reliable because of changing reCaptcha v2 to reCaptcha v3. \nReCaptcha v3 isn\'t reliable. There is not possible to submit form, because reCAPTCHA v3 says: error: reCAPTCHA v3 test failed. \n\nSometimes it is possible to sent form, but often it isn\'t possible. After testing it, 10 forms were submitted and 20 forms not. Now I\'m trying to sumbit form, but it is not possible. \n\nI can\'t risk, that clients can\'t write me. Moving to reCaptcha v3 should be optionable but not obligatory. Plugin is now unusable. Who wants website, which sometimes works and sometimes not? \n\nIf your website does not work, you see problem. You can solve it. But when you are using this plugin, you doesn\'t see problem. Website looks like pretty. But when are you clients trying to contact you, it is not possible. So you are loosing money. \n\nThis plugin is free, but with this problem is very, very dangerous and expensive. \n</div>\n</div>\n";}s:13:"download_link";s:63:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.5.1.1.zip";s:11:"screenshots";a:1:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:"src";s:67:"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454";s:7:"caption";s:16:"screenshot-1.png";}}s:4:"tags";a:5:{s:7:"contact";s:7:"contact";s:12:"contact-form";s:12:"contact form";s:5:"email";s:5:"email";s:8:"feedback";s:8:"feedback";s:4:"form";s:4:"form";}s:8:"versions";a:134:{s:3:"1.1";s:61:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.1.zip";s:4:"1.10";s:62:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.zip";s:8:"1.10.0.1";s:66:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.0.1.zip";s:6:"1.10.1";s:64:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.1.zip";s:3:"1.2";s:61:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.2.zip";s:3:"1.3";s:61:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.3.zip";s:5:"1.3.1";s:63:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.3.1.zip";s:5:"1.3.2";s:63:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.3.2.zip";s:3:"1.4";s:61:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.zip";s:5:"1.4.1";s:63:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.1.zip";s:5:"1.4.2";s:63:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.2.zip";s:5:"1.4.3";s:63:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.3.zip";s:5:"1.4.4";s:63:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.4.zip";s:3:"1.5";s:61:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.5.zip";s:3:"1.6";s:61:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.6.zip";s:5:"1.6.1";s:63:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.6.1.zip";s:3:"1.7";s:61:"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.7.zi